title: Bobby Reveals His Best Man + Bobby Offers $1000 For Stolen Property + Bobby Calls Out Ronnie Dunn!
itunes:title: Bobby Reveals His Best Man + Bobby Offers $1000 For Stolen Property + Bobby Calls Out Ronnie Dunn!
description:
Bobby reveals who will be the best man in his wedding! Bobby offers a reward after Caitlin’s grandfather's belongings were stolen while he was in the hospital battling COVID. We talk to Ronnie Dunn of Brooks and Dunn about his new music video, Lensmen project and the last text exchange between him and Bobby. Plus, Bobby plays a famous 2000's TV theme song and the crew has to guess the show!
